Package nl.pim16aap2.animatedarchitecture.core.tooluser.stepexecutor

@NonNullByDefault package nl.pim16aap2.animatedarchitecture.core.tooluser.stepexecutor
Contains the StepExecutor class and its subclasses.

Step executors for several types are provided, but more can be defined when needed.

A step executor generally accepts an object of a specific type and then provides it as input for a Function.
